_aChangeLog.text: Radar on top left corner (will be easier to not get lost)
Changed the shape of windows and wall to improve on rendering, and reduce unneeded geometry
Removed incorrect optimization tools- hints and occluders (back then I didn't know how to correctly use them)

_aLatestUpdates._sText:
See the final 2 pictures for radar and building update

So first map updated! Only 3 to go! After that I will pack them all in a neat pack and publish project-wintermaze_2016 pack!!! Yay!!!

_sText:
I've been working on project ''Wintermaze2016'' For a while now. Here's the first of hopefully several maps!


players: 20vs20

Now I know what you'r thinking ''It's a goddamn maze!!'' But here me out please. The maze isn't meant to get you lost, that wasn't my goal. Heck, you can even walk straight thru it! Think of it more like a series of protective walls to prevent players from getting sniped. 

With that being said I hope that you will enjoy the map and have fun! :)

 P.S. This map has it's secrets. So keep your eyes open!
